Validate ``const`` fields.
The value provided for a ``const`` field must be equal to the default value of the field. This is to support the keyword of the same name in JSON Schema.

Assume IPv4Network initialised with a default ``strict`` argument
See more: https://docs.python.org/library/ipaddress.html#ipaddress.IPv4Network

Assume IPv6Network initialised with a default ``strict`` argument
See more: https://docs.python.org/library/ipaddress.html#ipaddress.IPv6Network

Perform a simple check if the value is callable.
Note: complete matching of argument type hints and return types is not performed
